           #DYSQLA QJL0451 XQJL0451-CA

      *@1.4 호출결과　확인
           EVALUATE TRUE
               WHEN COND-DBSQL-OK
               WHEN COND-DBSQL-MRNF
                    CONTINUE
               WHEN OTHER
      * 에러메세지 : 테이블 SELECT 오류입니다．
      * 조치메세지 : 전산업무담당자에게　문의바랍니다
                    #ERROR CO-B4200223 CO-UKJL0036 CO-STAT-ERROR
           END-EVALUATE

      *@1.5 출력변수 MOVE

           IF DBSQL-SELECT-CNT < CO-NUM-3
              MOVE ZERO
                TO DBSQL-SELECT-CNT
           END-IF

      *    출력건수                                                   02660024
           MOVE DBSQL-SELECT-CNT                                        02670024
             TO XDJL4045-O-OUTPT-LINE-CNT1                              02680024

      *    OUTPUT LOOP
           PERFORM VARYING WK-I FROM 1 BY 1                             02730024
             UNTIL WK-I > XDJL4045-O-OUTPT-LINE-CNT1                    02740024
      *        대분류업종코드명
               MOVE XQJL0451-O-LAG-C-BZTYP-CD-NAME(WK-I)
                 TO XDJL4045-O-LAG-C-BZTYP-CD-NAME(WK-I)
      *        산업관리한도
               MOVE XQJL0451-O-IDSTRY-MGT-CLAM(WK-I)
                 TO XDJL4045-O-IDSTRY-MGT-CLAM(WK-I)
      *        명목액기준한도
               MOVE XQJL0451-O-TTL-AMT-BASE-CLAM(WK-I)
                 TO XDJL4045-O-TTL-AMT-BASE-CLAM(WK-I)
      *        명목액기준잔액
               MOVE XQJL0451-O-TTL-AMT-BASE-BAL(WK-I)
                 TO XDJL4045-O-TTL-AMT-BASE-BAL(WK-I)
      *        TE한도환산금액
               MOVE XQJL0451-O-TE-LIMT-AUC(WK-I)
                 TO XDJL4045-O-TE-LIMT-AUC(WK-I)
      *        TE잔액환산금액
               MOVE XQJL0451-O-TE-BAL-AUC(WK-I)
                 TO XDJL4045-O-TE-BAL-AUC(WK-I)
      *        한도여유액
               COMPUTE XDJL4045-O-LIMT-SEXTR-AMT(WK-I)
                     = XDJL4045-O-IDSTRY-MGT-CLAM(WK-I)
                     - XDJL4045-O-TE-LIMT-AUC(WK-I)
      *        소진율
      *        산업관리한도가　０보다　크면　산출
               IF XQJL0451-O-IDSTRY-MGT-CLAM(WK-I) > 0
                  COMPUTE WK-EXHS-RT
                        = XQJL0451-O-TE-LIMT-AUC(WK-I) /
                          XQJL0451-O-IDSTRY-MGT-CLAM(WK-I)
                  COMPUTE XDJL4045-O-EXHS-RT(WK-I)
                        = WK-EXHS-RT * 100
      *        그렇지않은경우　０으로　산출
               ELSE
                  MOVE ZERO
                    TO XDJL4045-O-EXHS-RT(WK-I)
               END-IF
           END-PERFORM
           .
       S3100-QJL0451-CALL-EXT.
           EXIT.
